NHS England #COVID19 stats:

• 95% of deaths have a pre-existing condition
• Average age over 80
• 91% deaths over 60, only 1% under 40

Excluding those with pre-existing conditions:

• 3 deaths under 20
• 35 deaths under 40
• 294 deaths under 60
• 849 deaths under 80 https://t.co/NkQM0WGGgq
